<p>This week there were two main issues that took people’s attention, the latest Russian missile attack on Ukrainian infrastructure/power generation and the continuation of the Battle of Bakhmut by Ukrainian forces (when many people seem to be arguing that they should be withdrawn). Ive said quite alot about the latter during the past few weeks, so will start with the former before going back to Bakhmut.</p><figure><a href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff1263e5d-6b4f-4cc9-a7dc-b14279bf5528_1080x804.png" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://reader.miniflux. 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/RMbb8_c9yOvJJI8JP8Lt_q6xiuM016Hv_zEzTpOJiH8=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd184NDgsY19saW1pdCxmX3dlYnAscV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkZmMTI2M2U1ZC02YjRmLTRjYzktYTdkYy1iMTQyNzliZjU1MjhfMTA4MHg4MDQucG5n 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/_a-ZIS-LIBGBBYCzlKyf- 1272w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/k9nRB2JkBBpGHW2TXDjvv1DB9nABVxGM-WJ5ZzFaSBo=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd18xNDU2LGNfbGltaXQsZl93ZWJwLHFfYXV0bzpnb29kLGZsX3Byb2dyZXNzaXZlOnN0ZWVwL2h0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGc3Vic3RhY2stcG9zdC1tZWRpYS5zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tJTJGcHVibGljJTJGaW1hZ2VzJTJGZjEyNjNlNWQtNmI0Zi00Y2M5LWE3ZGMtYjE0Mjc5YmY1NTI4XzEwODB4ODA0LnBuZw== 1456w" sizes="100vw"/><img src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/GCmMI41RKcURjX3E4S1yz_" alt="Russia launches largest missile strike against Ukraine in months" title="Russia launches largest missile strike against Ukraine in months" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/PInDwUavqZ0lhYQPv2ANQuEs-HkM_V3HI-WJpAi35sw=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd180MjQsY19saW1pdCxmX2F1dG8scV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3R